@host = http://localhost:5145

### Test de conexion a Supabase
GET {{host}}/api/supabase/test

---

### Registrar nuevo cliente
POST {{host}}/api/clientes/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre_empresa": "Empresa Test",
  "correo_contacto": "test@test.com",
  "contrasena": "password123"
}

---

### Login de cliente
GET {{host}}/api/clientes/login?correo_contacto=test@test.com&contrasena=password123